{"name": "jinja2-strcase", "metadata": {"name": "jinja2-strcase", "version": "0.0.2", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Natural Language :: English", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 2", "Programming Language :: Python :: 2.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.4", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.5", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: CPython", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: PyPy"], "home_page": "https://github.com/marchmiel/jinja2-strcase", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["jinja2"], "summary": "A python package for converting string case in jinja2 templates", "upload_time": 1592758355}, "documentation": ["# jinja2-strcase\n\nA python package for converting string case in jinja2 templates (including cookiecutter).\n\nIt is a port of the go package [strcase](https://github.com/iancoleman/strcase)\n\n## Installation\n\njinja2-strcase is available for download from PyPI via pip:\n\n```\n$ pip install jinja2-strcase\n```\n\n## Example\n\n```\nfrom jinja2 import Environment\n\nenv = Environment(extensions=['jinja2_strcase.StrcaseExtension'])\n\n# This will convert 'Any kind of string' -> 'any_kind_of_string'\ntemplate = env.from_string(\"{% 'Any kind of string' |  to_snake }\")\n\ntemplate.render()\n```\n\n| Function                        | Result               |\n|---------------------------------|----------------------|\n| `to_snake`                      | `any_kind_of_string` |\n| `to_screaming_snake`            | `ANY_KIND_OF_STRING` |\n| `to_kebab`                      | `any-kind-of-string` |\n| `to_screaming_kebab`            | `ANY-KIND-OF-STRING` |\n| `to_camel`                      | `AnyKindOfString`    |\n| `to_lower_camel`                | `anyKindOfString`    |\n\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "jinja2_strcase", "documentation": ["-*- coding: utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "jinja2_strcase.__author__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jinja2_strcase.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "jinja2_strcase.StrcaseExtension", "xref": {"fqname": "jinja2_strcase.jinja2_strcase.StrcaseExtension", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "jinja2_strcase.jinja2_strcase", "documentation": ["-*- coding: utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [{"name": "jinja2_strcase.jinja2_strcase._space_numbers", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "match", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jinja2_strcase.jinja2_strcase._add_word_boundaries_to_numbers", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "string", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jinja2_strcase.jinja2_strcase._to_camel_init_case", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "string", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "init_case", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jinja2_strcase.jinja2_strcase.to_camel", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "string", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jinja2_strcase.jinja2_strcase.to_lower_camel", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "string", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jinja2_strcase.jinja2_strcase._to_screaming_delimited", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "string", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "delimiter", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "screaming", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "jinja2_strcase.jinja2_strcas